---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Best English Tutoring Platforms 2026: Complete Comparison"
  description="Compare the top 10 online tutoring platforms for learning English. Find the perfect match for your budget, goals, and learning style."
>
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="mb-8">
      <span class="text-sm text-neutral-400">Comparison · Updated April 2026</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-1 mb-4 text-slate-200">Best English Tutoring Platforms in 2026: Complete Comparison</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">Compare the top 10 online tutoring platforms for learning English. Find the perfect match for your budget, goals, and learning style.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Affiliate Disclosure (FTC Compliance) -->
    <div class="text-xs text-slate-600 mb-6 p-4 bg-amber-950/60 rounded-lg border border-amber-700">
      <strong>Affiliate Disclosure:</strong> LearnEnglish.Life may earn a commission when you sign up through links on this page, at no extra cost to you. Our recommendations are based on research, not payments.
    </div>

    <div class="bg-emerald-900/30 border border-emerald-700 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
      <p class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-white">Our Top Picks</p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-emerald-400">Best Overall</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-300">iTalki</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-indigo-400">Best for Beginners</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-300">Preply</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-blue-400">Best Budget</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-300">Cambly</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-purple-400">Best Structured</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-300">Lingoda</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4 text-slate-200">Top 10 Platforms at a Glance</h2>
    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
      <table class="w-full border-collapse">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-slate-200">
            <th class="border border-gray-400 p-3 text-left text-slate-200">Platform</th>
            <th class="border border-gray-400 p-3 text-left text-slate-200">Price</th>
            <th class="border border-gray-400 p-3 text-left text-slate-200">Tutors</th>
            <th class="border border-gray-400 p-3 text-left text-slate-200">Best For</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr class="bg-slate-900/60"><td class="border border-gray-400 p-3 font-bold text-slate-200">iTalki</td><td class="border border-gray-400 p-3 text-slate-700">$5-40/hr</td><td class="border border-gray-400 p-3 text-slate-700">10,000+</td><td class="border border-gray-400 p-3 text-slate-700">Budget, conversation</td></tr>
          <tr class="bg-slate-950/60"><td class="border border-gray-400 p-3 font-bold text-slate-200">Preply</td><td class="border border-gray-400 p-3 text-slate-700">$10-80/hr</td><td class="border border-gray-400 p-3 text-slate-700">50,000+</td><td class="border border-gray-400 p-3 text-slate-700">Structure, beginners</td></tr>
          <tr class="bg-slate-900/60"><td class="border border-gray-400 p-3 font-bold text-slate-200">Cambly</td><td class="border border-gray-400 p-3 text-slate-700">$9.99/mo</td><td class="border border-gray-400 p-3 text-slate-700">10,000+</td><td class="border border-gray-400 p-3 text-slate-700">Speaking practice</td></tr>
          <tr class="bg-slate-950/60"><td class="border border-gray-400 p-3 font-bold text-slate-200">Verbling</td><td class="border border-gray-400 p-3 text-slate-700">$15-50/hr</td><td class="border border-gray-400 p-3 text-slate-700">5,000+</td><td class="border border-gray-400 p-3 text-slate-700">Professional tutors</td></tr>
          <tr class="bg-slate-900/60"><td class="border border-gray-400 p-3 font-bold text-slate-200">Lingoda</td><td class="border border-gray-400 p-3 text-slate-700">$15-25/lesson</td><td class="border border-gray-400 p-3 text-slate-700">500+</td><td class="border border-gray-400 p-3 text-slate-700">Group classes, structured</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4 text-slate-200">Detailed Platform Reviews</h2>
    
    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3 text-slate-200">1. iTalki. Best Overall</h3>
    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">iTalki offers the best combination of price flexibility and tutor variety. Whether you want casual conversation practice or structured lessons, you can find it here. Starting prices from $5/hour make it accessible for learners on any budget.</p>
    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed"><strong>Rating: 9.2/10</strong></p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3 text-slate-200">2. Preply. Best for Beginners</h3>
    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Preply provides a structured learning path with homework, progress tracking, and curriculum-based lessons. Perfect for beginners who need guidance and accountability.</p>
    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed"><strong>Rating: 8.8/10</strong></p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3 text-slate-200">3. Cambly. Best Budget Option</h3>
    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Cambly's subscription model ($9.99/month) offers unlimited conversation practice with native speakers. Ideal for learners who want to practice speaking frequently without watching costs.</p>
    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed"><strong>Rating: 8.0/10</strong></p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3 text-slate-200">4. Verbling. Best for Professional Tutors</h3>
    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Verbling focuses on professional, vetted tutors with structured lesson plans. Higher prices but more consistent quality and professionalism.</p>
    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed"><strong>Rating: 8.4/10</strong></p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3 text-slate-200">5. Lingoda. Best Group Classes</h3>
    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Lingoda offers small group classes and corporate training. More expensive per lesson but includes group interaction and structured curriculum.</p>
    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed"><strong>Rating: 7.8/10</strong></p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4 text-slate-200">How to Choose</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Consider these factors when choosing a platform:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-slate-600 mb-6">
      <li><strong>Budget:</strong> iTalki and Cambly offer the lowest prices</li>
      <li><strong>Learning style:</strong> Preply for structure, iTalki for flexibility</li>
      <li><strong>Goals:</strong> Conversation practice vs. exam prep vs. business English</li>
      <li><strong>Schedule:</strong> Some platforms require booking in advance</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="bg-blue-900/30 border border-blue-700 rounded-xl p-6 mt-8">
      <p class="font-bold mb-2 text-white">Ready to start?</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-300">Compare prices and features in our detailed reviews above.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>
